WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:01.000 --> 00:00:04.000
While the work on the Hokkaido Shinkansen is in full swing,

00:00:04.000 --> 00:00:10.000
there is a station ending its about-24-year-long history.

00:00:17.000 --> 00:00:22.000
Shiriuchi Station on the JR Kaikyo Line

00:00:29.000 --> 00:00:34.000
It is the southernmost ground station located at northern entrance of the Seikan Undersea Tunnel.

00:00:41.000 --> 00:00:46.000
It is a small station which has only 4 stopping trains.

00:00:53.000 --> 00:00:58.000
It is a station which has few lights and sounds at nightfall.

00:01:05.000 --> 00:01:10.000
It is a station where passanger trains running under the Tsugaru Straits pass speedy.

00:01:17.000 --> 00:01:22.000
It is a station which sees major freight trains sedately.

00:01:29.000 --> 00:01:34.000
It is a station which was born as signal station and goes back to signal station.

00:01:34.000 --> 00:01:36.000
Special Movies of Shiriuchi Station

00:01:36.000 --> 00:01:39.000
1. The Last Winter of Shiriuchi Station on the JR Kaikyo Line

00:01:39.000 --> 00:01:44.000
2. 14 Trains Passing through Shiriuchi Station on the JR Kaikyo Line

00:01:44.000 --> 00:01:52.000
2 Movies are going to post at 18:00(JST) on 14th February, 2014, at the same time.

00:01:52.000 --> 00:01:54.500
As a passenger station, here disappears. But as a signal station, here remains.

00:01:54.500 --> 00:01:56.500
After opening of Shinkansen, please come again.

00:01:56.500 --> 00:02:00.000
said by a local towner of Shiriuchi

